overview: Hitchhiker Jillian Janson sneaks onto a farm to find a bale of hay to crash on for the night. Bliss Dulce is desperate for a new car, but her cheap mother won't buy her one. Playful and horny, Misha Cross wants to play a game of hide and seek in the woods. Cassidy wants to watch TV. Keiran wants to play video games. Luckily, they both want to fuck. When Alina West gets busted for breaking and entering, she shows her chump friends just how hardcore she can be, promising Mark Ashley the ride of his life if he'll let her trespassing slide. When Darla Crane gets home and sees her stepson Logan Pierce filming a homemade sex tape with his new girlfriend Alice Green, she's not mad.
title: Young And Corrupt: Anal Edition
